    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Vessel rattles of Hawaii made from a small gourd containing seeds or pebbles, fitted with a handle surmounted by a circular ruff of feathers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
